Next, an eNB in the embodiment of the present invention will be described. Referring to FIG. 6, an embodiment of the eNB of the present invention includes:
a selecting unit 601 configured to select a second subframe from a plurality of subframes when a data packet transmitted by a UE in a first subframe is not correctly received;
a signaling transmitting unit 602 configured to transmit a scheduling signaling to the UE, so that the UE transmits a retransmission packet of the data packet in the second subframe selected by the selecting unit 601.

Specifically, please referring to FIG. 7, another embodiment of the eNB of the present invention includes:
a selecting unit 701 configured to select a second subframe from a plurality of subframes when a data packet transmitted by a UE in a first subframe is not correctly received;
a signaling transmitting unit 702 configured to transmit a scheduling signaling to the UE, so that the UE transmits a retransmission packet of the data packet in the second subframe selected by the selecting unit 701.

Specifically, please referring to FIG. 8, another embodiment of the eNB of the present invention includes:
a selecting unit 801 configured to select a second subframe from a plurality of subframes when a data packet transmitted by a UE in a first subframe is not correctly received;
a signaling transmitting unit 802 configured to transmit a scheduling signaling to the UE, so that the UE transmits a retransmission packet of the data packet in the second subframe selected by the selecting unit 801.

claim.claim-text:
The method according to claim 7, wherein the scheduling signaling is an UL_grant signaling;

the transmitting, by the UE, the retransmission packet of the data packet in the second subframe indicated by the scheduling signaling according to the scheduling signaling comprises:
acquiring, by the UE, indication information for indicating the second subframe and contained in the UL_grant signaling;
determining, by the UE, the second subframe according to the indication information; and
transmitting, by the UE, the retransmission packet of the data packet in the second subframe.

The method according to claim 7, wherein the scheduling signaling is an UL_grant signaling;

the transmitting, by the UE, the retransmission packet of the data packet in the second subframe indicated by the scheduling signaling according to the scheduling signaling comprises:
acquiring, by the UE, transmitting time or carrier of the UL_grant signaling;
determining, by the UE, the second subframe according to the transmitting time or carrier of the UL_grant signaling; and
transmitting, by the UE, the retransmission packet of the data packet in the second subframe.

The UE according to claim 15, wherein the scheduling signaling is an UL_grant signaling;

the retransmitting unit comprises:
a first acquiring module configured to acquire indication information for indicating the second subframe and contained in the UL_grant signaling;
a first determining module configured to determine the second subframe according to the indication information acquired by the first acquiring module; and
a first transmitting module configured to transmit the retransmission packet of the data packet in the second subframe determined by the first determining module.

The UE according to claim 15, wherein the scheduling signaling is an UL_grant signaling;

the retransmitting unit comprises:
a second acquiring module configured to acquire transmitting time or carrier of the UL_grant signaling;
a second determining module configured to determine the second subframe according to the transmitting time or carrier of the UL_grant signaling acquired by the second acquiring module; and
a second transmitting module configured to transmit the retransmission packet of the data packet in the second subframe determined by the second determining module.
